    "Typst source": "Typst de origen",
    "= Welcome to Typst\n\nWrite *Typst* here — headings, _emphasis_ and math are all supported.\n\n$ integral_0^1 x^2 dif x = 1/3 $\n\n- One\n- Two\n- Three\n\n한국어도 잘 표시됩니다 — Paper Tools": "= Bienvenido a Typst\n\nEscribe *Typst* aquí — títulos, _énfasis_ y matemáticas son compatibles.\n\n$ integral_0^1 x^2 dif x = 1/3 $\n\n- Uno\n- Dos\n- Tres\n\n한국어도 잘 표시됩니다 — Paper Tools",
